%h2 TSV
%p The IANA have published a very vague specification around TSV that you can read <a href="http://www.iana.org/assignments/media-types/text/tab-separated-values">here</a>.
%ol
  %li
    %p The <b>first</b> record in a TSV file may contain column names for each of the fields, separated by TABS.
  %li
    %p Fields are not allowed to have embedded TAB characters.
  %li
    %p Fields with embedded double-quote characters must be enclosed within double-quote characters, and each of the embedded double-quote characters must be represented by a pair of double-quote characters.
